data.description: Beautiful Sparks single story home. Light and bright floorplan with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a 3 car garage. Great location close to schools, parks and shopping.  Other features include:  Granite counters, new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, new upgraded pine kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances, high ceilings, large storage shed, & stamped concrete patio.  No HOA.
